summary: An Imperial Female aptly named Sky
descriptionHtml:
An Imperial Female aptly named Sky
(Changed file name to avoid confusion, sorry to those looking for a sky Mod)

The Mods used to create her were:
No Dirty Bodies - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=18
Detailed Faces - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26
Beautiful Girls - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=475
Forsworn armor - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=208
No more blocky Faces - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
Ultra Smooth - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140

I realize that a few of these textures overlap.
author: Skycatcher
